'''Tau''' was a letter in the [[Tionese/Legends|Tionese alphabet]]. Tau was often used as a [[Callsign/Legends|call sign]] for [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Flight group/Legends|flight groups]], specifically [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]] and [[Missile Boat]]s. Missile Boat designated ''Tau 1'' was one such example.

The [[Force Hound]] [[Tau (individual)|Xesh]] was named Tau, which meant "soul" in his native language.

